query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (n.name like '%n%' OR n.name like '%x%' OR n.name like '%V%' OR n.name like '%g%' OR n.name like '%r%') AND n.gender in ('f') AND pi.note not like '%Jade SinClair PR%' AND pi.note not like '%Katy Monahan Huntley%' AND cn.name not like '%20th Century Fox%' AND cn.name not like '%STX%' AND cn.name not like '%Amblin Partners%' AND cn.name not like '%A24%' AND cn.name not like '%Miramax%' AND cn.country_code not in ('ge','ne','gh','sz','an','me') AND mi.info in ('Japanese','Polish','Mandarin') AND cct1.kind in ('complete+verified','complete','crew')
